  "name": "RPlog_Zeebok_s_Great_Escape",
  "title": "An Underground Passage for Mr. Zeebok",
  "summary": "On Theseus Station, the fixer Zeak introduces the freelance hauler Jaspar Andromidas to Mr. Zeebok, a Nikto seeking passage to Ord Mantell and an introduction to Ambassador Delgard, alongside the B'omarr Monk Hugo, who will run such extra-legal operations going forward. Jaspar accepts the job and an additional contract to deliver aid products and a forged document to Drax Rendolen. The smuggler rendezvouses with Drax aboard the Arcadia in an asteroid cluster, handing over the medical aid and the forged CSA undercover security credentials in exchange for seventeen thousand credits. Finally, Jaspar lands at the Ord Mantell starport, where Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard receives Zeebok, paying Jaspar fifteen thousand credits via a palmed credstick while maintaining the fiction that the Nikto is merely new crew. With the handoff complete, Ambrosia escorts the weary Zeebok toward a waiting speeder, a warm meal, and the next stage of his underground passage.",
